edu.byu.oit.core.cmis.CMISInterface

Interface IObjectPathModel

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    ObjectPathModel

    public interface IObjectPathModel
    A data modelling class that holds and object name, path, and type. This is used primarily in the Cmis API to upload folders, where it was necessary to keep information about local objects and folder in one spot, and distinguish between types.
